## Summary

Systems engineer with 10+ years of experience designing and delivering complex
hardware/software systems for defense and aerospace programs. Active TS/SCI clearance.
Strong background in requirements decomposition, integration testing, and cross-functional
team leadership. Experience with MBSE, DoDAF, and Agile/SAFe methodologies.

