## Skills

Engineering: Systems engineering, requirements analysis, interface control documents (ICD),
MBSE, SysML, DoDAF, trade studies, risk management, FMEA, V&V planning

Software/Tools: MATLAB/Simulink, Python, DOORS, Jira, Confluence, Git, MS Project

Domain: Space systems, satellite communications, radar, electronic warfare, C4ISR

Leadership: IPT lead, proposal writing, earned value management (EVM), subcontractor management

